              = inline_svg "check.svg", class: "h-4 w-4"
          p.text-gray-600.mb-6
            | Start managing your projects immediately with our hosted solution.
          .bg-gray-100.border-2.border-black.p-4.mb-6.relative
            / Decorative corner
            .absolute.-top-2.-right-2.w-4.h-4.bg-pink-300.border-2.border-black
            ul.text-sm.text-gray-700.space-y-2
              li • Free for all while in development
              li • No credit card required
              li • Import / Export data
              li • Community support available
          a.bg-blue-500.text-white.px-8.py-4.border-4.border-black.hover:bg-blue-600.transition-all.font-bold.text-lg.inline-flex.items-center.justify-center href="https://app.iteratorpm.com/users/sign_up"
            | Sign Up
            = inline_svg "arrow-right.svg", class: "w-6 h-6 ml-4"

